{
  "texts": [
    "We excluded any clusters where more than 25% of the abstracts contained EC or ENC contexts.",
    "TF-IDF analysis was then conducted on each cluster to further differentiate noise terms.",
    "These noise terms were eliminated from the raw CarD-T -NER labeled entities.",
    "The CD-TF-IDF procedure eliminated 2,203 classified entities.",
    "Among the remaining uniquely classified entities, we consolidated all synonyms with an in house algorithm, Synonym-Lustre, a tool for synonym disambiguation in biomedical terminology."
  ]
}